alternateQuestions.question: What is the charge if I cancel my ticket

answer.text: The cancellation charges depend on the airline, sector, class of booking, and time of cancellation.

faqs.question: I need to cancel my flight, what’s the fastest I can do this by

alternateQuestions.question: How fast I can cancel my airline ticket

faqs.label:
I need to cancel my flight, what’s the fastest I
can do this by

answer.text: you can cancel your flight no later than 3 hours before the time of departure.

An e–ticket (electronic ticket) is a paperless electronic document with a unique confirmation number that neatly replaces the hassles of a paper ticket. When you purchase an e–ticket, we email it to you after the
booking is complete. Simply print it out and bring it with you – along with a valid photo ID to the airline counter when checking in for your flight.

faqs.question: How to get my E-Ticket details

alternateQuestions.question: How do i know my E-Ticket details

faqs.label: How to get my E-Ticket details

answer.text: We’ll send your e–ticket details to the email address you gave us when you made your reservation.

faqs.question: How do I know my reservation was booked
faqs.label: How do I know my reservation was booked

answer.text: We’ll send you an SMS and an email to confirm your flight booking.
